## Task 2: Update work-with-me.tsx

Read `/c/Users/flori/src/techbyflo/client/src/pages/work-with-me.tsx`

Rewrite the key sections to match the new offer:

1. Update the main headline to: "Trabaja con Flo — Experto en Privacidad Digital para Autónomos"
2. Update product descriptions to match the new offers (Auditoría Gratis, Blindaje Básico, Guardia Digital)
3. Fix the self-linking CTA (currently links to same page) — change it to link to `/quiz` 
4. Fix checkout URLs to use `import.meta.env.VITE_CALENDLY_URL ?? "#"` instead of `VITE_LS_BASIC_URL`
